1.患者女性，63岁，既往高血压病史5年，最高峰值：160/106mmHg，未规律服药，脑梗死病史3年，否认糖尿病病史。2.主要特点：头晕，伴有视物旋转，劳累及情绪激动加重，甚则如坐舟船，平卧后好转，右侧肢体疼痛麻木，肿胀刺痛，固定不移，夜间痛甚，按之较硬，屈伸不利，有硬结，发无定时，时有耳鸣，无发热及畏寒，无肢体及语言活动障碍，无恶心及呕吐，无腹泻等症状。3.查体：T&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;'&gt; 35.5℃，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;'&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;P80&lt;/span&gt;分&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;、R18&lt;/span&gt;次∕分&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;、BP150/100mmHg，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;'&gt;咽部无充血，两侧扁桃体无肿大，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: 楷体_GB2312;'&gt;口唇无紫绀，颈软无压痛，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 24px; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;颈部活动受限，屈曲30&deg;，伸展30&deg;，左侧屈35&deg;，右侧屈30&deg;，左旋转50&deg;，右旋转55&deg;，平卧位及体位变化时不适加重&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;，臂丛神经牵拉试验、头部叩击试验及椎间孔挤压试验均阳性，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-langua